quran[15]{c,v,t}:
  23,28,"“Uye kana mapinda mungarava, iwe neavo vanewe, taura kuti: ‘Rumbidzo ngaive kuna Allah, avo vatidzivirira kubva kune vanhu vanotadza.’”"
  23,29,"“Uye taura kuti: ‘Tenzi vangu! Itai kuti tive tinomira panzvimbo yakakomborerwa, uye ndimi munokwanisa kutiburutsa zvakanaka.’”"
  23,30,"Zvirokwazvo, mazviri (zvatakaita vanhu vaNowa) mune zviratidzo, uye zvirokwazvo, tinogara tichiedza varanda vedu"
  23,31,Uye takave tinosika vamwe vanhu mushure mavo
  23,32,"Uye takatuma mutumwa kubva kwavari achitaura kuti: “Namatai Allah! Hamuna umwe mwari kusara kwavo. Saka hamuvi munotya here (kuti vachakurangai kana mukanamata zvimwe zvinhu)?”"
  23,33,"Uye avo vakakwirira (vapfumi, vatongi) pakati pevanhu vake avo vasina kutenda, uye vakaramba kuti kuchasanganwa mushure mekufa, uye takavapa kugarika kwehupenyu hwepasi, vakataura kuti: “Uyu haasi (chimwe chinhu) asi kuti murume akafananawo nemi. Anodya izvo zvamunodyawo, uye anonwa izvo zvamunonwa.”"
  23,34,"“Uye\tkana\tmukateerera\tmunhu\t(murume)\takaitawo\tsemi,\tzvirokwazvo,\tmuchava munorasikirwa.”"
  23,35,"“Anokuvimbisai here kuti kana mafa mova munoita ivhu nemapfupa, kuti muchave munomutswa (zvakare)?”"
  23,36,"“Zviri kure, zviri kure, izvo zvamunovimbiswa!”"
  23,37,"“Hapana chiripo kusara kwehupenyu hwedu hwepasi rino, tichafa uye tinorarama! Asi hative tinomutswa zvakare (mushure mekufa)!”"
  23,38,"“Haasi umwe munhu asi kuti murume aronga manyepo pamusoro paAllah, uye hatimbofi takatenda maari.”"
  23,39,"Akataura kuti: “Tenzi vangu! Nditsigirei nokuti vave vanondiramba.”"
  23,40,"(Allah) vakataura kuti: “Munguva shoma, zvirokwazvo vachave vanodemba.”"
  23,41,"Nokudaro murango wakavaparadza muchokwadi, uye takaita kuti vave marara sezvidyarwa zvakafa. Nokudaro ngavave kure avo vanhu vanotadza"
  23,42,Uye takasika mamwe marudzi mushure mavo